  "special": {
    "title": "Fandir? Thirteen.",
    "description": "Adds extra critical hit damage (scales) on top of Jakobs shotgun crit.\n\nExtremely accurate with increased ADS zoom and a tiny spread, but notably higher recoil and slightly reduced base damage."
  },
  "notes": "Zer0 gains little over a same-level purple Scattergun, but the precision helps land pellets on weak points.\n\nSalvador: reliable ranged damage even when firing from the hip.\n\nGaige: strong with Anarchy; mag size can hit 1 for easy stacking, accuracy offsets penalties, and it can proc frequent novas with Shock and AAAGGGGHHH!.\n\nAxton: likes recoil control (eg Metal Storm, Steady).\n\nJakobs grip can reach 4 rounds, handy for crystalisks.\n\nHigh crit suits Nisha's Showdown; some Luneshine rolls can push crit further.",
